  "notes": "The homing reload throw is strong against flying enemies and is useful for reload-throw challenges. Shots fired in mid-air can receive amp damage, but they do not benefit from every stealth-style damage bonus. It will not lock on to cloaked targets until they are revealed. With high reload speed you can have several throws active at once. The final blast is boosted by grenade damage bonuses.",
